{{Quote|So even as you die again and again, I shall return! Born again in this endless circle that I have created!|Chaos}}
'''Chaos''' is the main antagonist and [[final boss]] of the original ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. He is found at the deepest part of the past [[Chaos Shrine (Final Fantasy)|Chaos Shrine]].

